Firm Overview 

We are staff-owned, committed to our independence, and we do only one thing: growth investing.







Founded: 1992
Ownership: 100% Staff Owned


Total Staff: 113
Investment Team: 37


Investment Style: Concentrated Growth
Investment Process: Independent, Bottom-up, Research-driven







