Sands Capital Management LLC
Home › Sands Capital Management LLC
Sands Capital Management LLC exclusively focuses on investing in high-quality growth businesses. The firm manages assets for a wide range of tax-exempt and taxable clients, including institutional pension plans, Taft-Hartley plans, endowments, foundations, families and individuals. The Arlington, Virginia-based firm has been a registered investment advisor since 1992.

"Our mission is to add value and enhance the wealth of our clients with prudence over time."
- Sands Capital Management LLC


