Sands Capital
































SANDS CAPITAL





Contact
Documents

















 Sands Capital exists to add value and enhance the wealth of our clients with prudence over time. Learn More >







Firm Overview

 We believe owning a concentrated portfolio of leading growth businesses is the best way to deliver on our mission. Learn More >







People & Culture

 Since our founding in 1992, Sands Capital's client-centered, research-driven culture has been closely guarded and nurtured by every staff member. Learn More >













Approach

We believe over time common stock price appreciation follows the earnings power and growth of the underlying business.

Learn More >




Process

Our research team applies our rigorous, criteria-driven, business-focused process as it strives to identify high quality growth businesses that are leaders in their fields. 

Learn More >




Strategies

We express our single investment philosophy primarily through our four flagship concentrated growth equity strategies: our U.S.-based Select Growth, Global Growth, Global Leaders and Emerging Markets Growth portfolios.

Learn More >



























